{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Tiny moves, building big picture stuff!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy the simple magic of combining three matching tiles to make your city bigger and better. With an added sprinkle of strategy. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customize Your Town with Unique Themes!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781880/extras/themes.gif?t=1728656866\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our variety of themes lets you build a town in your ideal aesthetic, including festive options like Halloween and Christmas! </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Have we mentioned night mode?</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781880/extras/nightmode.gif?t=1728656866\" />  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you a dark mode gremlin? Us too! Switch to Night Mode and watch as your city grows &amp; glows under the stars. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>No rush</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No timers or stress. Merge, build, and expand at your pace, crafting your city your way. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Chill Out with our Lo-Fi Tunes and Low-Poly Art</strong></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781880/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728656866","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781880/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1728656866","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781880/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728656866","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781880/c